uld be set.  One of the lamest things this game has is camp disputing, and this I am sure all of us agree on.  When I first heard of this I was alittle surpised, since I have not read any offical posting on this.  What I suggest is for all the clerics that need ragefire to meet one day.  Let the clerics work it out among themselves...for this is a cleric issue.  Everyone here posting their opinions and thoughts is fine, but end results is the needs and wants of the clerics that should decide what happens.<br>There should be rules set though to this list.  An example would be if cleric #1 on the list is not present then the second cleric can form up a dragon killing after x minutes waiting.. blah blah.  If the cleric community wants this to work, they should band together and set rules for this.  Hopefully as a whole we ease the stress of the clerics in our guilds.  I know way too many clerics get dishearted at the thought of their epic.  As a guildleader or officer you should know the personal pain a cleric goes through when it comes to this part.  Afterall this is just a game.<br><br>Just my thoughts,<br>Zarax Solonari<br>Leader of Undivided Faith<br>   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/uenaliya.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Enaliya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>THogg's Lubba</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/23/02 5:08:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3100.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Cleric Ragefire List</span><hr size=1> Hmm, I  know for a fact there are several TK clerics that are waiting for rage as well. Saela for example has waited 4 months to the best of my personal knowledge. I like the idea but you may wanna check with a few other guilds if that idea is going to truely work o